<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Strathcona Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">According to information gathered in 2006, the community is mostly made up of detached single-family homes (making up 81.5% of real estate in the community), with the remaining 18.5% being condominiums and attached homes. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">About 7.2% of the homes in the community are occupied by renters.</p>
        </div>
